.h1 Signup or Signin

- if flash[:must_be_signed_in]
  .notice You must be signed in to do that! Signin or signup below - it's free and easy!
- if flash[:donated]
  .notice 
    Thanks for your donation! If you signup or signin now your account will be updated to allow you to save wods. If you run into any problems just shoot us an email at
    %a{ :href => "mailto:crossfitwodder@gmail.com" } crossfitwodder@gmail.com
    and we'll get the situation resolved asap.

#signupin
  .signup.grid_6.alpha
    .sub signing up with Wodder is free and easy as filling out the form below!
    .h2 Signup
    = render :partial => "user_form", :locals => { :user => @user, :signup => true }

  .signin.grid_6.omega
    .sub already have an account?
    .h2 Signin
    = form_for @user, :url => signin_users_path do
      - if flash[:signin_error]
        %ul
          %li Invalid email password combo.
      %div
        %label
          Email
          %div= text_field_tag "email"
      %div
        %label
          Password
          %div= password_field_tag "password"
      %div
        = submit_tag "Signin"
